      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"Display&amp;SampleFiltersinKatana-SettingupDisplayandSampleFiltersinKatana\">Setting up Display and Sample Filters in Katana</h3><p>Create <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661887/Sample+and+Display+Filters\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661887\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Display and Sample Filters</a> in Katana with Material or with PrmanShadingNodes.  Assign the Material or NetworkMaterial to <code>/root</code> with a MaterialAssign node.  </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"728\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178680/rfkSampleFilterMaterialAssign.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=563&amp;height=309\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178680/rfkSampleFilterMaterialAssign.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"309\" data-width=\"563\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178694\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkSampleFilterMaterialAssign.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178680\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"ea33b376-ed2b-433d-ba22-3c454a85266f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178680/rfkSampleFilterMaterialAssign.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=563&amp;height=309 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178680/rfkSampleFilterMaterialAssign.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535174&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=563&amp;height=309 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"Display&amp;SampleFiltersinKatana-UsingMultipleDisplayorSampleFilters\">Using Multiple Display or Sample Filters</h3><p>You can use PxrSampleFilterCombiner or PxrDisplayFilterCombiner and a ShadingNodeArrayConnector node to combine multiple Sample or Display Filters. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"458\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178680/rfkMultipleSampleFilters.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=458&amp;height=399\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178680/rfkMultipleSampleFilters.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"636\" data-width=\"729\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178697\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkMultipleSampleFilters.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178680\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"f68b31bf-47bf-4045-a7ec-1049aa89de89\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178680/rfkMultipleSampleFilters.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=729&amp;height=636 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178680/rfkMultipleSampleFilters.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531535175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=458&amp;height=399 1x\"></span><p />"
